                    <msContents>
                        <summary>A woodblock printed manual on the care of young infants based on lectures given by Hazama Sōgen and written down by four of his followers, published in 1817. The text is in hiragana-majiri with extensive furigana, but all the prefatory material including the introduction is in kanbun with no kunten. In a section on childhood palsy Hazama quotes at length from Yi xue yuan liu lun (醫學源流論), a study of the origins of medicine by Xu Dachun (徐大椿) (1693-1771), adding kunten to the original Chinese text. Also included is an illustration of a child with hydrocephalus and some of Hazama’s written diagnoses in his own hand, which are reproduced in the form of a negative (white text on a black background). </summary>

                        <textLang mainLang="ja" source="IANA">Japanese</textLang>

                        <msItem n="1" xml:id="Japanese_118">

                            <author key="person_16626011" source="VIAF">
                                <persName type="original" xml:lang="ja">羽佐間宗玄</persName>
                                <persName type="standard" xml:lang="ja-Latn">Hazama Sōgen</persName></author>

                                <title type="original" xml:lang="ja" source="IANA">老婆心書</title>
                                <title type="standard" xml:lang="ja-Latn" source="IANA">Rōba shinsho</title>
                                <title type="standard" xml:lang="en" source="IANA">Guidance for midwives</title>
                            

                            <filiation><p>See <ref target="https://kokusho.nijl.ac.jp/?ln=en">Kotenseki Work ID: 1029227</ref> for copies of 老婆心書 held by other institutions.</p>
                            </filiation>

                            <note>封面に「羽佐間先生口訣／桜寧軒蔵板」とあり。巻頭に「門人／東都森宗哲／会津蓮沼栄碩／浜松田辺玄樹／備中松山鈴木三悦／交述」とあり。（奥付） 老婆心書続編近刻／文化十四丁丑歳秋七月／書肆／京、植村藤右衛門／大坂、河内屋吉兵衛／東都、鴨伊兵衛。両冊裏表紙に墨書「于時昭和三年／土佐姓蔵」。</note>

                        </msItem>

